# Cursor adapter — Xiao Liu Ren

This skill lets the Cursor agent perform a Xiao Liu Ren reading.

## Hard rules
1. Never invent the cards / hexagram / position. Run the CLI:
   ```bash
   ai-divination xiaoliuren --method numbers --month 3 --day 12 --hour 7
   ```
   (Omit `--seed` for real readings; seeded mode is for tests and reproducible demos only.)
2. Parse the JSON output. Interpret using `../SKILL.md` plus
   `../references/interpretation-template.md`.
3. Refuse medical / legal / financial / emergency / crisis advice — see
   `../../../shared/safety-policy.md`.

## When to trigger
Cast Xiao Liu Ren for quick timing reflection.

## Default example
> Is now a good moment to send this message?
